774
00:55:27,908 --> 00:55:30,326
Hah? tas saya.

775
00:55:30,327 --> 00:55:31,994
Aku meninggalkan tasku.

776
00:55:31,995 --> 00:55:34,038
Aku akan pergi dan mengambilnya…

777
00:55:34,039 --> 00:55:35,207
