780
00:55:41,964 --> 00:55:43,549
Ayo.

781
00:55:54,226 --> 00:55:55,686
Saya juga baru saja pulang kerja.

782
00:55:57,312 --> 00:55:58,771
Oh.

783
00:55:58,772 --> 00:56:00,648
