784
00:56:00,649 --> 00:56:02,109
Tentu, mari kita bertemu.

785
00:56:02,818 --> 00:56:05,945
Tapi, Tuan Cha, apakah Anda berjalan ke sini?

786
00:56:05,946 --> 00:56:08,864
Wah, itu sangat dekat. Sampai jumpa jam 10--

787
00:56:08,865 --> 00:56:10,993
